pageContext.claim: “So interesting that, when I announced Trump National Doral in Miami would be used for the hosting of the G-7, and then rescinded due to Do Nothing Democrat/Fake News Anger, very few in Media mentioned that NO PROFITS would be taken, or would be given FREE, if legally permissible!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump's claims about "no profit" and "zero cost" should be taken with a grain of salt, considering that he does not release his tax returns or Trump Organization financial statements to the public and admitted in legal proceedings before he was president that he employs guesswork and boasts when giving estimates.
